# CloudBox

CloudBox is a secure cloud storage and management platform.

## Features
- File upload/download
- Automated backup
- CLI or Web interface
- Docker-based easy deployment

## Technologies
- Python or Node.js
- Docker
- AWS S3 / Azure Blob / GCP Storage
- Terraform / Ansible (optional)

## Installation
```bash
git clone https://github.com/tulinakdnz/cloudbox.git
cd cloudbox
docker-compose up -d







